{"tid":634701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"恆管2學生涉校內藏毒被捕","createTime":"2018-04-19T12:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T13:07:14.000Z","uid":90538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39d666b455d5aeab3cdeae817a8a5269e4faaf69","tid":634701,"uid":90538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"恆生管理學院有2名學生涉嫌在校內藏毒，在職員報案後，警方到學校宿舍調查，拘捕該2名學生。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，恆生管理學院在本月12日（上周四）凌晨，有學生在校內懷疑吸毒，被警方拘捕。警方發言人回覆本報查詢時表示，本月12日凌晨約2時，接獲沙田行善里一院校職員報案，指懷疑有人在學生宿舍房間內吸食毒品。警員到場後，在現場檢獲少量懷疑大麻草及懷疑毒品吸食工具，並拘捕兩名分別21歲及22歲男子，涉嫌管有危險藥物。二人獲准保釋候查，須於下月底向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n恆管確認，在4月12日凌晨，校方發現學生宿舍房間有少量懷疑大麻草，即時報警處理。警方事後帶有關人士返警署協助調查。校方強調，非常重視學生操守及宿舍管理，對於任何涉嫌違規行為，都會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524132885931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524132885931&d=odlsMY%2FUvJxbsnYOIisLTARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=87a2c47e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524132885931&h=277491ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524132885931</a>"},{"pid":"65b18308442536029e1d9489f74fbc900ee46e33","tid":634701,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"恆大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c923803986e962e1cbf4dca9a0e89929d0fa590","tid":634701,"uid":32527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"抄登仔俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e39bbff640eba36bcddab4416940f11116589b","tid":634701,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T1